result.name: Wu Kong Shanghai Restaurant

reviews.text:
Quality Shanghaiese restaurant at prime location in Tsim Sha Tsui. The food quality are at top level for Shanghai cuisine. 響鈴火腿夾 及  拔絲香蕉Are the must try items. The only complaint is that the lag time between dishes are just too long. It took total 2 hours for 8 dishes...

If you are going to drive, the nearest public parking is at K11 but personal preference is harbour city.
good menu and food! They have a MobileApp which always surprise you with special and discount coupons. If you fancy something for afternoon tea, this is where you should go!
Food quality and price is reasonable
Not a WOW kind of place but you leave with your tummy feeling comfy

Service is good, food is average. But they do provide a wide selection of cuisine. One of the authentic Shanghainese restaurant in Tsim Sha Tsui.  I went there Tuesday night and the tables are almost fully occupied, was a bit surprised! Looks like a popular spot.

result.name: 滬江飯店

reviews.text: 超值好味😋
食物水準越來越差😾

日本人向け…の、上海蟹のコースをいただきました。日本人向け、というと、びっくりするくらい割高な価格設定のお店が多い中、とても良心的なお値段でした。どの料理もとても美味しかったです。
蟹はお店の方が素早い手つきで綺麗に解体、してくれます。地元の方がほとんどのランチタイムでした。
価格、メニューのバランス、味、雰囲気、どれも満足のいくものでした。
ぜひまた伺いたいです。

很久沒來滬江飯店了，到尖沙咀即興試一下有沒有位。
2人點了3個菜，點的都是人從前沒在這吃過的，共$5××多元。
這個辣椒滿滿的麻辣魚，魚肉嫩滑， 辣味不會太重麻的感覺比較多。
雖舊不如前，可惜！但都不失為一間招牌老店
